testcase.name: should call BluetoothGatt.readRemoteRssi() exactly once when run()
should emit an error if BluetoothGatt.readRemoteRssi() returns false
should emit and error if RxBleGattCallback will emit error on getOnRssiRead() and release queue
should emit exactly one value when RxBleGattCallback.getOnRssiRead() emits value
should timeout if RxBleGattCallback.onReadRssi() won't trigger in 30 seconds
